<h1>BlazorBasics InputFileExtended Component</h1>
<h2>Version 3.5.22</h2>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col">
        <p>
            This component extend the functionality about traditional <string>InputFile</string>.<br />
            Has many properties to customize and also events to manage.<br />
            <a class="btn btn-success" href="get-started">Get Started</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<p>From version 3.5.22 supports a Func to send the files to the server, don't uset HttoClient anymore. Allow copy and pase and/or drag and drop. Show a list with files upload for user can remove if change mind without reload page and or without programmer need to manage.'.</p>
